Interface JPPFNodeTaskMonitorMBean

  • All Superinterfaces:
    NotificationBroadcaster, NotificationEmitter

    public interface JPPFNodeTaskMonitorMBean
extends NotificationEmitter
    MBean interface for task-level monitoring on each node.
